        "subject": "LU-7404 zfs: Reset default zfs version to 0.6.5.5",
        "message": "LU-7404 zfs: Reset default zfs version to 0.6.5.5\n\nIt turned out the I/O timeout was related to the storage on\nHyperion, and the workaround solution is to reduce maximum\ndirty data ZFS can cache in memory by setting:\n\n  options zfs zfs_dirty_data_max=<value>\n\nThis patch will propose Lustre to use latest ZFS release from\nupstream.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Icfaecce4dfa91da6632dc90b265aff87f022a166\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_8"
    }
